title: WATCH: Coach Urban Meyer Talks New Book On CBS This Morning
text:
WATCH: Coach Urban Meyer Talks New Book On CBS This Morning By 10TV Web Staff Monday October 26, 2015 8:55 AM UPDATED: Monday October 26, 2015 10:35 AM NEW YORK - 
Fresh off his 150th career win, the Ohio State University Head Football Coach Urban Meyer appeared on CBS This Morning to discuss his new book, Above the Line: Lessons in Leadership and Life from a Championship Season . Coach Meyer also discussed the Buckeyes unexpected trip to the National Championship in January of 2015 and safety concerns for players of all ages.
